  "detailed_description": "Transform into your Mega Gunship boss form to blast your rival head-on in this unique shooting game with a competitive twist.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/654100/extras/RMG04.jpg?t=1523430116\" ><br><br>Rival Megagun is a competitive split-screen vertical shmup (or shoot 'em up, shooting game, STG) where you transform into a gigantic boss ship - your &quot;Mega Gunship&quot; - to invade your opponent's screen. Build up your chain and unleash devastating attacks. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/654100/extras/RMG_Mega.jpg?t=1523430116\" ><br><br>Multiple heroes to choose from, each with their own set of special weapons and Mega Gunship form. Features intense 2-player local and online versus battles and a single-player arcade mode.",
